About this item

  • Duvet cover set is prewashed for a sumptuously soft feel and it gets softer and softer with every wash.
  • Woven with 152TC cotton, that retains also less heat.and in a strong, tight weave for durability.
  • Comforter Cover with quality zippered closure and four interior corner ties to keep it in place.
  • Full/Queen set comes with 1 duvet cover (104"x90"), 2 shams (20"x36"). (Duvet insert NOT included)
  • Wash Care: Machine washable, normal cycle with like colors. Only Non-Chlorine Bleach. Tumble dry low.

Product description

LOVQUE Cozy Cotton Duvet Covers are available in the six most popular colors. Below characteristics of duvet cover deliver ultimate comfort:

  • 100% Cotton front.
  • 100% Cotton Back.
  • Yarns made with 100% cotton fibers, delivering softness and durability.
  • A Prewashed processing that is soft to the touch.
  • Strong, not flimsy or easily worn out, because of the tight, one-over-one plain weave.
  • Cotton fibers wick away moisture, making 100% cotton sheets extremely breathable.
  • Duvet Cover: Button closure; 4 interior corner ties keep it in place.
  • Popular colors to complement living room decor

Twin Size Duvet Cover Set:
Duvet Cover: 68"(W) x 90"(L) x 1, Pillowcase (20"x26") x 1

Queen Size Duvet Cover:
Duvet Cover: 90"(W) x 90"(L) x 1, Pillowcase (20"x26") x 2

King Size Duvet Cover:
Duvet Cover: 104"(W) x 90"(L) x 1, Pillowcase (20"x36") x 2

How are ratings calculated?
